des:
Now you'll be able to control your Alokium lights and devices with your Alexa!
No more using the switch or even your hands! Just speak to your Alexa and she'll handle everything for you!

To use this feature, you'll need to connect Alexa to your Alokium devices as follows:
(1) Download the "Alokium" app from your app store;
(2) Register your account using an email address;
(3) You should have Alokium devices on hand;
(4) Install your devices and configure them through the Alokium App, giving them names that will be spoken when using the skill;
(5) Download the Amazon "Alexa" app from your app store;
(6) Set up your Alexa device in the app;
(7) Look for the "Alokium" skill in the Skills tab of the Alexa app;
(8) Click Enable Alokium Skill and you will be redirected to the login screen;
(9) Enter your account details and password.
(10) Done! The entire setup is now complete;

Now you're ready to use commands such as:
"Alexa, turn on the bedroom light."
"Alexa, turn off the bedroom light."
"Alexa, set the brightness of the bedroom light to 50 percent."
"Alexa, increase the brightness of the bedroom."
"Alexa, decrease the bedroom light by 50."
"Alexa, change the bedroom light to green."
